{
  "stem": "2996.5",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it tells what's going on in Germany and so on and so forth.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "If I were to-- I would have too much trouble looking at table of contents with a magnifying glass in order to tell you what's inside.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I have to be satisfied with that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But one of the things which financed my operation-- no, that's not the right-- one of the things-- some of the money I collected was used to publish the first book in German, different chapters written by different people, about their experiences in the concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Two of the writers later became acquaintances of mine.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "One of them started publishing a weekly German newspaper in Chicago.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then the other one was a member of the Reichstag, which is-- was the German house of Parliament, which Mr.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Hitler burned down in order to get more votes in the then upcoming election.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Because he did not have control of the Parliament.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He needed a few more votes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So one of the things they did is they burned the Reichstag and said, this is what the Communists did.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So vote anti-communists.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Vote for us.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Now that book I got from my sister.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And when Spielberg received an honorary degree from the University of Southern California, for which I worked, I gave that book to somebody to give to the president of the university, who presented it as a memo to Spielberg.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I included in it a few of the typical pro-Nazi anti-Semitic leaflets, so that he would have an idea of what-- what is behind it.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know what you mean by-- by surveillance.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, again, through the same man that I mentioned to you earlier, who gave me the Ku Klux Klan study.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was real active there.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
